        <item>
            <title>Apple Store 首尔弘大店开幕　成为亚太区第 100 间分店</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/21/apple-store-hongdae/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-store-hongdae</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/21/apple-store-hongdae/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 13:00:34 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Store]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[韩国]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1216267</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 在韩国第 7 间 Apple Store 终于开幕，位于弘大的这间零售店也是亚太区的第 100 间 Apple Store。<br /><span id="more-1216267"></span></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1216276" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/applehongdaeseoulope-694x462.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/applehongdaeseoulope-694x462.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/applehongdaeseoulope.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Apple 表示，Apple Store 首尔弘大店将会成为学生、家庭和当地社区提供服务，包括产品发售、售后支援以及各种 Today at Apple 讲座。弘大店附近就是弘益大学以及梨花女子大学，一向都是年青人聚集的地方，今次 Apple 在当地设立新店铺，也是方便学生购入产品，新开张优惠活动中，就主打学生选购 Mac 或 iPad 时可以特价购入 AirPods 或 Apple Pencil 的优惠。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1216278" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/applehongdaeseoulmed-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/applehongdaeseoulmed-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/applehongdaeseoulmed.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>除了新开张优惠，他们还邀请 Hip-Hop 歌手 Beenzino 驻场提供 Today at Apple Pop-Up Studio 活动，指导参加者用 iPad 的 Freeform App 制作 2024 愿景图。韩国一向是 Apple 苦战的市场，尤其是当地消费者相对更喜欢本地品牌如 Samsung 和 LG 等，直到近年情况才逐渐改变。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2024/01/apple-hongdae-now-open-in-south-korea/">Apple</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/21/ipad-air-12_9-cad-leaked/notebook/tablet-notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">传闻 iPad Air 12.9 吋版本，机身设计图网上流传</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/20/netflix-youtube-spotify-no-vision-pro-app/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">加入「制裁」Apple 行动    YouTube、Spotify 不推 Vision Pro 专用 App</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/18/netflix-apple-vision-pro/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Vision Pro 不会有 Netflix 专用 App    用户只可用 Safari 观看</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/21/apple-store-hongdae/fun-tech/">Apple Store 首尔弘大店开幕　成为亚太区第 100 间分店</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/21/apple-store-hongdae/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
